response.original_title: j'ai mis ma bite dans une canette
response.overview: The main character (unnamed man #34) lives in a none described apartment. He desires to put his male reproductive system into a can of Chef Boyardee’s Beefaroni. Unfortunately he could only get his hands on was Ravioli. The man decides that it will have to work. After a lot of wides shots and cuts to random women reacting to things, unnamed returns to his home. He opens the can (this takes 1hr 63 minutes), and places him self inside of it. He then wakes up in a mental asylum and hangs himself. He again wakes up but this time he’s Hitler at the end of WW2, and his glasses break before he can read a book.
response.tagline: I can’t believe I ate the whole thing!
